body_html: I can't reproduce duplicate registration errors, at least from Python (which is just a thin wrapper around TF_LoadLibrary). For example adding a bunch of extra tf.load_op_library calls from //tensorflow/user_ops:ackermann_test seems to work fine (on Linux). Is there something else I should be looking for?
